---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Enia - The Future">
	<main>
		<section class="hero fade-in">
			<h1>The <span class="gradient-text">Future</span> of <br/> Cellulose Intelligence</h1>
			<p class="subtitle">Experience the tactile revolution. Zero latency. Infinite resolution. 100% Biodegradable.</p>
			<div class="cta-group">
				<a href="#features" class="btn primary">Explore Technology</a>
				<a href="/contact" class="btn secondary">Pre-Order Sheet</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="features" class="features fade-in">
			<div class="card float" style="animation-delay: 0s;">
				<h2>Quantum-Ready Surface</h2>
				<p>Our proprietary wood-pulp matrix is compatible with all analog writing instruments, offering 0ms input lag.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card float" style="animation-delay: 1s;">
				<h2>Zero-Energy Retention</h2>
				<p>Once data is inscribed, it remains visible for centuries without a power source. The ultimate cold storage.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card float" style="animation-delay: 2s;">
				<h2>Haptic Experience</h2>
				<p>Feel the data. Our textured interface provides real-time physical feedback for every pixel.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="quote fade-in">
			<blockquote>"It's like a tablet, but lighter. And it smells like a forest."</blockquote>
			<cite>â€” Elon M. (No relation), Visionary CEO</cite>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	main {
		margin: auto;
		padding: 4rem 2rem;
		max-width: 1200px;
		color: var(--color-text);
	}

	.hero {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 8rem 0;
		min-height: 80vh;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
	}

	h1 {
		font-size: 4rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		line-height: 1.1;
	}

	.gradient-text {
		background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-secondary));
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
	}

	.subtitle {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto 3rem;
		color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.8);
	}

	.cta-group {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.btn {
		padding: 1rem 2rem;
		border-radius: 4px;
		font-family: var(--font-heading);
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	.btn.primary {
		background: var(--color-primary);
		color: var(--color-bg);
		box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 243, 255, 0.4);
	}

	.btn.primary:hover {
		box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(0, 243, 255, 0.6);
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}

	.btn.secondary {
		border: 1px solid var(--color-primary);
		color: var(--color-primary);
	}

	.btn.secondary:hover {
		background: rgba(0, 243, 255, 0.1);
	}

	.features {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		padding: 4rem 0;
	}

	.card {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		transition: transform 0.3s ease;
	}

	.card:hover {
		border-color: var(--color-primary);
		box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 243, 255, 0.1);
	}

	.card h2 {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		color: var(--color-primary);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.quote {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 6rem 0;
		font-style: italic;
	}

	blockquote {
		font-size: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		color: var(--color-paper);
	}

	cite {
		font-size: 1rem;
		color: var(--color-secondary);
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		h1 {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
		}
		.cta-group {
			flex-direction: column;
		}
	}
</style>
